    "This outcome suggests that enhanced memory capabilities often result in superior generation outcomes.",
    "In order to achieve the best results, TRIME (Zhong et al., 2022) used the IWSLT'14 De-En baseline.",
    "Given that the task is sentence-level, the researchers did not use local memory and long-term memory, as there are few repetitive tokens in them.",
    "Instead, they used only external memory, which enabled them to beat the KNN-MT (Khandelwal et al., 2020) in performance.",
    "As the RALM architecture continues to evolve, an increasing number of potential application directions are being identified."
